手靚牌我地，唔跟只有輸<br />\n控訴中共違反聯合聲明，香港脫離邪惡政權統治之路！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1513362\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1513362</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HZMuHc0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHZMuHc0.png&h=25e1e5b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d744347f1b63a9acc9f8a212b39eb5516ec0725","tid":1487362,"uid":190161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:59:56.000Z","msg":"龜咁慢點捕蚊？飛天龜都唔夠蚊快啦下嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6dc20ae9a87585ae1879d2753d2bb2c38dcbf32","tid":1487362,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d744347f1b63a9acc9f8a212b39eb5516ec0725","tid":1487362,"uid":190161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:59:56.000Z","msg":"龜咁慢點捕蚊？飛天龜都唔夠蚊快啦下嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:26:56.000Z","msg":"有人講咗係食水入面啲卵同幼蟲"}]}